<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-giJF6kkoqNQ00vy+HMDP7azOuL0xtbfIcaT9wjKHr8RbDVddVHyTfAAsrekwKmP1" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <title>내 정보</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">메인</a></li>
            <li><a href="/dashboard">대시보드</a></li>
            <li><a href="/update">정보 수정</a></li>
            <li><a href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a></li>
            <li><a href="/withdrawal">회원탈퇴</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">안녕, {{user.name}}</h5>
                <p class="card-text">당신의 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
                <a href="mailto:{{user.email}}?Subject=Hello" target="_top" class="btn btn-primary">{{user.email}}</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="display-4">내 정보 페이지입니다.</h1>
                <p class="lead">더 많은 것을 개발할 예정입니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ygbV9kiqUc6oa4msXn9868pTtWMgiQaeYH7/t7LECLbyPA2x65Kgf80OJFdroafW" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>